    <!-- Manual Activity -->
    <string name="manual_title">User Manual</string>
    <string name="print_manual">Print Manual (PDF)</string>
    <string name="manual_content"><![CDATA[
        <h3>1. DETECTION SYSTEM</h3>
        <p>DSA monitors the environment using your device microphone to identify the specific high-pitched acoustic signatures of drone motors and propellers.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><b>Modes:</b> Choose between standard FFT Frequency Analysis or Advanced AI (TensorFlow Lite).</li>
            <li><b>Visualizers:</b> Choose between <b>Spectrogram</b> (waterfall history) or <b>Oscilloscope</b> (real-time wave peaks). Both show detection threshold lines.</li>
            <li><b>States:</b> Scanning (Listening), Verification (Analyzing), Triggered (Warning), and Sleep (Cooldown).</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>2. MICROPHONE & AI SETUP</h3>
        <p>Fine-tune how the app hears the environment:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><b>Input Source:</b> Choose between internal microphones, Bluetooth headsets, or a <b>Local Audio File</b>.</li>
            <li><b>Audio File Mode:</b> Select a .wav or .mp3 file to test detection logic in a loop. Ideal for bench testing.</li>
            <li><b>Audio Gain:</b> Increases sensitivity for detecting targets at longer distances.</li>
            <li><b>Noise Gate:</b> Filters out background hum and static noise.</li>
            <li><b>AI Analysis:</b> Replaces peak detection with neural pattern recognition to filter out birds, wind, or planes.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>3. GPS JAMMING & INTERFERENCE</h3>
        <p>DSA tracks satellite health to detect spoofing or electronic interference.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><b>Jamming Score:</b> A 0-10 rating. Scores 4+ trigger an alert. Based on signal power (C/N0), satellite drops, and fix stability.</li>
            <li><b>Baseline Mapping:</b> Establish a reference level by recording for 30-60s in a clean area.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>4. LOCAL ALERTS</h3>
        <p>Immediate feedback methods on the device:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><b>Sound:</b> Select a custom alarm tone from your device.</li>
            <li><b>Flashlight:</b> Rapidly flashes the camera LED 5 times upon detection.</li>
            <li><b>Vibration:</b> Haptic feedback for tactical or noisy environments.</li>
            <li><b>Delay &amp; Cooldown:</b> Set how many seconds a drone must be heard before triggering, and how long to wait before the next alert.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>5. REMOTE ALERTS</h3>
        <p>Automated notifications to external systems:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><b>Email:</b> Supports SendGrid or SMTP. Can include GPS coordinates, timestamps, and Google Maps links.</li>
            <li><b>Rsyslog:</b> Sends structured JSON payloads (event, time, coordinates, debug data) over UDP or Secure TLS.</li>
            <li><b>SMS:</b> Automatic text alerts to your contact list.</li>
            <li><b>Bluetooth:</b> Send trigger strings to paired external devices via SPP.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>6. LOGGING &amp; OPTIMIZATION</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><b>Debug Logs:</b> Dedicated logs for Email and Rsyslog to troubleshoot errors.</li>
            <li><b>Keep Screen On:</b> Highly recommended to ensure CPU remains at full speed.</li>
            <li><b>Night Vision:</b> Tactical theme to preserve night vision in the field.</li>
        </ul>
    ]]></string>

